<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Fitness Hub</title>
  <link rel="icon" href="icons/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
  <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Karla:wght@350;400;600;700;800&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/partials/header.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/app.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include("./partials/header") %> 
  <%- include("./partials/flash") %> 
  <div class="container-top">
    <div class="motto-container">
      <div class="motto-text">
        <h2>Fitness starts</h2>
        <h2>with what you eat.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="motto-descrip">
        <p>Take action by tracking calories and</p>
        <p>breaking down ingredients with Fitness Hub.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="motto-button">
        <a href="/signup">Start For Free</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="eat-right">
      <img
        src="https://res.cloudinary.com/domad5jvw/image/upload/v1653236797/FitnessHub/oatmeal_bowl_zomqx6.png"
        alt="Eat Right"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container-top row-reverse">
    <div class="motto-container">
      <div class="motto-text">
        <h2>Meet</h2>
        <h2>expectations.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="motto-descrip">
        <p>Track your macros, calories, vitamins, and overall nutrition
        in foods all through Fitness Hub to meet your desired goals.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="eat-right">
      <img
        src="https://res.cloudinary.com/domad5jvw/image/upload/v1653237076/FitnessHub/Eggs_bmpurv.png"
        alt="Eat Right"
      />
    </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container-top">
      <div class="motto-container">
        <div class="motto-text">
          <h2>Learn from</h2>
          <h2>real experiences.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="motto-descrip">
          <p>Learn from blog posts that contain ingredients, recipes, personal stories and their adventures.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="eat-right">
        <img
          src="https://res.cloudinary.com/domad5jvw/image/upload/v1653237063/FitnessHub/onions_vknu8j.png"
          alt="Eat Right"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="search-div">
        <div class="search-content">
          <h1 class="search-title">Search foods for nutritional information.</h1>
          <div class="search-box">
            <form action="/food">
              <input class="search-input" type="text" name="search" placeholder="Apple" autocomplete="off">
              <button class="search-button" href="#">
                <i class="search-icon">&#8981;</i>
              </button>
            </form>
          </div>
          <div class="search-info">
            <div class="info-box">
              <p>Search through thousands of foods with the Food Central database.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="info-box">
              <p>Access calories, nutrients, and food portions.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="info-box">
              <p>Log food in your food diary to keep track of what you eat.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="benefits-div">
      <h2 class="benefits-title">Benefits of Fitness Hub</h2>
      <div class="container-benefits">
        <div class="panel-advantage">
          <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/domad5jvw/image/upload/v1653236662/FitnessHub/Eating_healthy_food_2_c0yiet.gif" alt="">
          <h3>Health</h3>
          <p>Get an understanding of why certain foods may not fit in your lifestyle, to better suit your goals.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-advantage">
          <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/domad5jvw/image/upload/v1653236685/FitnessHub/Diet_2_pjoyfx.gif" alt="">
          <h3>Progression</h3>
          <p>Finally see results by getting the right amount of nutrition.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-advantage">
          <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/domad5jvw/image/upload/v1653236625/FitnessHub/Personal_Trainer_2_rb9vpn.gif" alt="">
          <h3>Motivation</h3>
          <p> Stay motivated by tracking what you eat, and learn your eating habits.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="benefits-button">
        <a href="/signup" class="start-button">Start Now</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="recipe-div">
      <div class="recipe-content">
        <h2 class="recipe-title-div">Fitness Hub Recipes</h2>
        <div class="post">
          <% for (let i = 0; i < 3; i++) {%>
              <figure class="recipe">
                      <img class="thumbnail" src="<%= recipes[i].image.thumbnail %>" alt="">
                      <div class="recipe-title-div-2">
                          <h2 class="recipe-title"><%= recipes[i].title %></h2>
                      </div>
                      <a class="link" href="/recipes/<%= recipes[i]._id %>">View Recipe</a>
              </figure>
          <% } %>
  </div>  
      </div>
    </div>
